column5: Yikes!! Stay off for another week.. someone will go through on the weekend for sure
Thanks Steve Yikes!! Stay off for another week.. someone will go through on the weekend for sure Hope it dosent happen, but something tells me you are right saddly..
Chip Chip step.. chip chip step, some just don't heed that advise.

Great video, good info for those thinking of venturing out.  I remember Paul, Terry and I went out on Cook's bay and they were on 4 inches, I was on two.  We didn't realize it at first, then Paul said something about it and we left.  You just never know!
or just stay off all together until it is safe...especially given the weather forecast for the next few days....
or just stay off all together until it is safe...especially given the weather forecast for the next few days....  Best advice in this thread.
